{"tid":623874,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"我只想唱歌俾大家聽","createTime":"2018-04-10T10:39:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T01:33:41.000Z","uid":132678,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1a5f187d1c620ff41cbedbae4bb120224898dfdb","tid":623874,"uid":132678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:39:43.000Z","msg":"因為我怕下面介紹自己會講左好多<br />\n所以虛線前係懶人包<br />\n我只係想自己可以COVER一D自己 鍾意既歌 / 覺得好既作品 俾大家聽，<br />\n而自己好多時主要都係唱廣東歌，<br />\n就算幾少都好，希望可以為本土音樂盡一點點綿力。<br />\n希望大家會LIKE我既YOUTUBE CHANNEL / FACEBOOK PAGE，<br />\n希望大家可以多多支持。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nYOUTUBE CHANNEL：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9XMOyuxdRPJS7jVY9N-nTw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUC9XMOyuxdRPJS7jVY9N-nTw&d=4NKuUjOPDzp%2FoMqKj1UAQQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=578272fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9XMOyuxdRPJS7jVY9N-nTw</a><br />\n<br />\nFACEBOOK PAGE：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MOONMANMUSIC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMOONMANMUSIC%2F&d=4NKuUjOPDzp%2FoMqKj1UAQQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=a7821533\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/MOONMANMUSIC/</a><br />\n<br />\nEMAIL：<br />\n[url]moonmanmusic01@gmail.com<br />\n[/url]<br />\n--------------<br />\n<br />\n在呢到再詳細少少介紹下自己<br />\n小弟其實自小以來主要都係唱歌為興趣<br />\n你問我既夢想，相信香港好多人都係一樣<br />\n當然係想做一個歌手，而且自己一直有學唱歌。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而小弟一直以來都有一個小小既理想，<br />\n就係可以開一個平台、有一個地方去SHARE自己 唱/翻唱 既歌俾人，<br />\n其實呢個世代要做呢件事的確唔難，<br />\n但多年以來有好多原因令自己冇咁做到，<br />\n包括自己既能力技巧、器材技術、私人理由等。<br />\n自己亦都唔想好求其咁交到一D野出黎就算。<br />\n<br />\n工作左數年，有時候覺得生活真係好苦悶，<br />\n亦覺得其實都可以嘗試一下俾人聽聽自己一直以來努力既野，<br />\n我唔敢話自己已經唱得有如天皇巨星，<br />\n但最起碼希望做到有人會聽，甚至有人可以見證自己未來既成長。<br />\n<br />\n除左學唱歌，小弟都有接觸唔同既樂器，<br />\n但都只係識少少，亦都有同朋友偶然出下SHOW去唱歌，<br />\n甚至學過下少少編曲作曲，<br />\n但我可以敢講自己現時真完全係冇呢方面既天份同能力，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n曾經好想開呢個平台係可以重新編寫、<br />\n用更好既音質既音樂去錄製翻唱再俾大家，<br />\n但可惜結果都係唔成功，而且好失敗。<br />\n曾經亦搵過一D同學/朋友合作，可惜大家都好忙，<br />\n亦都好難好自私咁，要人地義務唔收錢咁去為你做好多野(如編曲、後製等)。<br />\n所以到最後都只能夠用網上一D MMO去錄，<br />\n如果將來有機會，有更好既能力及技術，希望可以帶更好既質素俾大家。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實一直以來，身邊好多朋友都叫我，<br />\n＂不過試下放下上網俾人聽啦＂，<br />\n其實自己一直亦都好想咁做，而上面亦都講左有好多原因令自己卻步。<br />\n<br />\n經過一番既準備同思考，總算可以勉強做到少少。<br />\n雖然仲有好多問題，例如網上版權既問題始終唔算好熟識，<br />\n只希望能夠邊做邊學。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而今次其實我係完全冇通知過任何一個朋友，<br />\n甚至冇通知身邊既家人親戚會在呢個時候做呢個平台去俾人聽。<br />\n所以你分分鐘會做左我第一個網上既聽眾。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有機會的話會再分享自己更多，<br />\n最後講多句，只要有一個人支持，<br />\n我都會繼續去努力學、繼續去努力做、繼續去努力唱。<br />\n<br />\n如有疑問，可以留言或以各種方式PM我，<br />\n可以回答既我都會盡力回答，多謝。<br />\n希望大家會LIKE我既YOUTUBE CHANNEL / FACEBOOK PAGE，<br />\n希望大家可以多多支持。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nYOUTUBE CHANNEL：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9XMOyuxdRPJS7jVY9N-nTw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUC9XMOyuxdRPJS7jVY9N-nTw&d=4NKuUjOPDzp%2FoMqKj1UAQQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=578272fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9XMOyuxdRPJS7jVY9N-nTw</a><br />\n<br />\nFACEBOOK PAGE：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MOONMANMUSIC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMOONMANMUSIC%2F&d=4NKuUjOPDzp%2FoMqKj1UAQQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=a7821533\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/MOONMANMUSIC/</a><br />\n<br />\nEMAIL：<br />\n[url]moonmanmusic01@gmail.com[/url]"},{"pid":"998ae632e696df55fd83b00ac2fe52763850a0ae","tid":623874,"uid":144784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:40:26.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"6190de195e83e1ab72fe7ddf914fd909e2a95166","tid":623874,"uid":132678,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:55:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LVFEtMNJXog\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLVFEtMNJXog&d=4NKuUjOPDzp%2FoMqKj1UAQQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=cadeb787\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LVFEtMNJXog</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/paZPP6XORzk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpaZPP6XORzk&d=4NKuUjOPDzp%2FoMqKj1UAQQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=9af6c639\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/paZPP6XORzk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HdKlBiOGNTE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHdKlBiOGNTE&d=4NKuUjOPDzp%2FoMqKj1UAQQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=7d16bbfc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HdKlBiOGNTE</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C1qCBkNO6C8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC1qCBkNO6C8&d=4NKuUjOPDzp%2FoMqKj1UAQQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=43a2aac0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/C1qCBkNO6C8</a>"},{"pid":"19a292e5f4c5caedcca6f94545906d03cd65104f","tid":623874,"uid":132678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:26:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf4728ea08927395ce72f59828fccd755502eca","tid":623874,"uid":168534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:29:09.000Z","msg":"垃圾簡體字<br />\n不了"},{"pid":"a545265bb02fa773fb4f52e5a2fd574cfb56410d","tid":623874,"uid":35557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:44:27.